rows.label: qst710502_msg0003
rows.name:
Have you defeated all the unique
monsters in Gula and Iira?

rows.label: qst710502_msg0005
rows.name:
I never thought this would be
achieved in my lifetime...

rows.label: qst710502_msg0006
rows.name:
I was thinking I might have to have my
grandchildren take over in the worst-case
scenario, but I'm overcome with emotion...

rows.label: qst710502_msg0007
rows.name:
The Great Encyclopedia of
Alst's Unique Monsters will
finally be complete...

rows.label: qst710502_msg0008
rows.name:
This should become a valuable
resource 100, 500 years from now.

rows.label: qst710502_msg0009
rows.name:
Thank you, everyone. I thank you
from the bottom of my heart.
